Lab - Conversational Language Understanding - Adding Intents


The below can be used as an example on adding intents :

Intent name  --  Description

BookRoom -- User wants to book a room
CancelBooking -- User wants to cancel an existing booking
ModifyBooking -- User wants to change an existing booking
CheckAvailability -- User wants to know if rooms are available
AskAmenities -- User asks about hotel facilities (e.g., pool, wifi)
CheckInTime -- User asks about check-in or check-out times
Greet -- User greets the assistant


Lab - Conversational Language Understanding - Adding Entities

The below can be added as entities :

Entity name -- Example values

RoomType -- single, double, suite, deluxe
CheckInDate -- July 12th, tomorrow, next Monday
CheckOutDate -- July 15th, Friday, in two days
GuestCount -- 1 guest, 2 adults, family of 4




Lab - Conversational Language Understanding - Adding Utterances


The below can be added as utterances :

Intent: BookRoom
I want to book a double room from July 12th to July 15th for 2 adults.
Can you reserve a suite for me tomorrow night?

Intent: CancelBooking
I need to cancel my reservation with booking number ABC123.
Can you cancel my room for July 15th?

Intent: ModifyBooking
I want to change my check-in date to July 13th.
Can I upgrade my room to a suite?

Intent: CheckAvailability
Do you have rooms available on July 20th?
Are there any double rooms open next weekend?

Intent: AskAmenities
Do you have free wifi?
Is there a gym in the hotel?

Intent: Greet
Hi
Hello





Lab - Custom Question Answering - Edit the knowledge base


The following examples of Q and A’s can be added to the knowledge base :

Q: How do I make a hotel reservation?
A: You can make a reservation directly on our website by selecting your
destination, travel dates, and number of guests.

Q: What is your cancellation policy?
A: Our standard cancellation policy allows free cancellation up to 24 hours before check-in.

Q: Do you offer airport shuttle service?
A: Yes, we offer complimentary airport shuttle service for all guests.

Q: What amenities are included with my stay?
A: All guests enjoy free Wi-Fi, complimentary breakfast, access to the fitness
center, and use of our swimming pool.

Q: How can I modify my existing reservation?
A: You can modify your reservation by logging into your account on our website
and selecting ‘Manage Booking.’

